<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Instructions - UExam</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/exams/instructions.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/media/favicon.ico">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="/media/ChitkaraUniversityLogo.png">
        <h1 class="heading">UExam - Test Management System</h1>
    </div>
    <h1 class="quiz-instructions">Quiz Instructions</h1>
    <hr>
    <ul>
        <h3>
            <li>There are total 20 MCQ's</li>
            <li>Each MCQ has only one correct answer</li>
            <li>After attempting the first page click on <u>Next</u> to move to next page.</li>
            <li>After attempting all the questions click <u>Submit</u> to submit the quiz</li>
            <li>After submission you can view your score by clicking <u>View result</u></li>
            <li>If you want to clear all selected answer click on <u>Reset</u></li>
        </h3>
    </ul>
    <hr>
    <form action="/test/attempt">
        <input id="checkbox" type="checkbox" required/>
        <label for="checkbox"> I have read the instructions carefully.</label>
        <br>
        <br>
            <div class="container">
                <button type="submit">Next &raquo;</button>
            </div>
    </form>
</body>
</html>